data.description: Sunshine streams in this luxurious home in The Ranch. Large Chef's kitchen w/ Butlers Pantry opens to spacious family room with fireplace and wall of windows. Formal living room and dining room. LVP flooring downstairs. 4 spacious bedrooms up include gorgeous master suite and XL bonus room over the garage for all your fun activities. Easy commute locationKitchen has gas range, new microwave, 2 ovens, granite countertops and 42" cabinets.  New water filtration system. Master bedroom has fireplace and a garden soaker tub for warming up on cold Alaska nights.   Laundry room and extra storage off garage. Washer/Dryer can stay.
